00:00:42,450 --> 00:00:45,200
 Ho Seok, wait. I can explain everything. 

9
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:47,090
 Bastard! 

10
00:00:47,090 --> 00:00:48,940
 Explain what? 

11
00:00:48,940 --> 00:00:51,350
 Embezzling the company's money? Or... 

12
00:00:51,350 --> 00:00:53,900
 dragging my father's foundation into getting an illegal loan? 

13
00:00:53,900 --> 00:00:56,970
 Or blowing all that money! 

14
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:01,530
 I was just trying to do my best. 

15
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:05,160
 I wanted to make the new business successful... 

16
00:01:05,160 --> 00:01:07,540
 Do you think I knew it would go sideways like this? 

17
00:01:07,540 --> 00:01:10,180
 Stop making excuses! 

18
00:01:12,780 --> 00:01:15,230
 It's all over. 

19
00:01:25,570 --> 00:01:28,890
 Life can be so funny. Right, Ho Seok? 

20
00:01:28,890 --> 00:01:31,400
 Gyeong Tae... 

21
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:33,400
 It seems like it was yesterday I messed up the company 
   

22
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:36,600
 and had to run off because of your dad. 

23
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:38,600
 And now, his son is coming to me 

24
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:42,000
 and asking me for money to save his business. 

25
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:45,700
 Please help me this one time. If not, our company— 

26
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:48,700
 - Even the school foundation could... 
 - I... 

27
00:01:48,700 --> 00:01:50,800
 have no intention of helping you. 

28
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:53,600
 Wait, Hyungnim... 

29
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:56,130
 Think of it as karma. 

30
00:01:56,130 --> 00:01:59,740
 Your father did the same thing to me. 

31
